The species was described on the basis of two males collected in "Hab. in Caucaso, Derbent" (photographs of original labels in 
Proshchalykinet al. 2017
). There are two males in ZISP from this locality, which corresponds to the original description of 
Morawitz (1872
, 
1874
). One of these males was designated as lectotype by Proshchalykin and Astafurova in 2016 (
Proshchalykin et al. 2017
).
